0. Install
pacman -S zen-browser-bin

1. Enable zen browser transparency:
browser.tabs.allow_transparent_browser = true
zen.widget.linux.transparency = true

2. Enable transparent style on most websites:
install 'Zen Internet' extension

3. Make Ctrl + T open a blank tab (instead of triggering the search bar):
zen.urlbar.replace-newtab = false
then also set New Tab to 'Blank Page' in settings and enjoy


Useful links:
https://www.reddit.com/r/zen_browser/comments/1ky8rdp/arch_hyprland_zen_browser/
